Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.18,0:00:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒甚麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請走這邊 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安女學園 山百合版灰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經用螢光筆作上了記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉紅色的是灰姑娘 藍色的是姐姐B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐B？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灰姑娘的壞心眼姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.26,0:00:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你不演灰姑娘時 希望你能演這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.93,0:00:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.47,0:00:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來你為甚麼會在這種地方吃午飯呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.55,0:00:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學正在逃避新聞部的采訪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.22,0:00:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我們學校的新聞部采訪的方法很強硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 接受念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.18,0:01:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就可以替你回答那些采訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.99,0:01:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.08,0:01:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願意的話 可以隨時來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.73,0:01:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還本想讓她同意在校慶時展示照片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 祥子大人討厭櫻花與銀杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.75,0:01:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才讓人吃驚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.68,0:01:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她竟然能堅持著到這裡來找祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.65,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.60,0:01:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.46,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.61,0:02:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒緩地行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.64,0:02:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.98,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}月與念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能請教一個問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,困難的問題可別找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼白薔薇大人會選志摩子同學做妹妹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.16,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很困難不過倒是很少見的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.01,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於選擇志摩子的原因一般不會有誰問到呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是因為志摩子同學\n看起來就像是應該被選中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我完全相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得這麼軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 我是稻秸嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.25,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白薔薇大人說的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對祥子大人來說 我是迎頭撞上並被抓住的稻秸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我還真佩服自己能比喻得這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稻秸 不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一點好呀？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被祥子一直握在手裡這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像志摩子這種人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得就該讓她為山百合會好好發揮其才能嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是剛才的問題的答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以白薔薇的身份回答的話 這個就是答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 以個人來說到還有其它的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.27,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否反倒是志摩子在羡慕著祐巳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 為甚麼會突然跳到那種話上啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看祐巳那可愛而又變化豐富的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等… 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然「長者」來了就到此結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.35,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 就是看見祥子進來才服務一下的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不快點洗杯子的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.66,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是大家快到這裡的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳真是一個好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓祥子嫉妒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我也該去看看樓下的情形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會穿上紅色的天鵝絨禮服去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我穿著平常的裙子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.90,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我要在有金色花卉圖案的披風上別上鑽石別針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 頭髮像這樣如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.94,0:06:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙杜瑞拉 你跟我們一起去舞會不是挺好的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是記得很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被白薔薇大人撫摸頭或擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也從未有過這麼強烈的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 剛才去取劇裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好像真的是正在忙碌中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在做劇本的練習而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要試穿服裝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天是試穿服裝與排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以花寺的學生會長也會過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經清楚地轉告過了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子也需要參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也該是去迎接的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 你能去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也就是花寺的學生會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該在正門那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跑 不能跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還會踩到銀杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 失禮了 請問是柏木同學嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山百合會的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是柏木優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天請多多關照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經確定能進入花寺的大學了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.07,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是附屬中學 若非成績優秀是不可能不參加考試就合格吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 能否在這裡稍等片刻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.99,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去換一下拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是讓人無法挑剔的王子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.06,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻被灰姑娘所討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.65,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我看錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人應該在薔薇館裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝各位的款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常漂亮的公館啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.04,0:08:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的學生會長 客觀地來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客觀來看 相當的不錯啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說作為祥子的對手沒甚麼不足的地方了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的戲劇其實還有另一個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是克服祥子的厭男症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子的家庭相當地複雜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖父與父親都在外面偷藏了女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人會討厭男人原來也是事出有由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 灰姑娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了句「我先去體育館」就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.35,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我也先去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才看見的果然是祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說已經回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.16,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.09,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在圖書館旁邊的路上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒去過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子會被弄髒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼祥子大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才剛注意到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.84,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實去過那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想早點看看對方的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.69,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想比對方更早地看到 就只有這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.12,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.23,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與花寺的學生會長跳舞的確非我本意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但逃避就意味著認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起其它任何東西 我最討厭的就是認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.18,0:11:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家到來之前 讓我來做你的舞伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用了 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是記住了舞步 但還無法跳得很流暢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算您這樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.38,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用想太多 信任自已身體的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別急躁 面帶微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.28,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.52,0:11:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.88,0:11:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 舞姿慢慢變得漂亮起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳舞原來是一件這麼愉快的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 我以前也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.74,0:12:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫小笠原 請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請你多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.96,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很帥氣吧 柏木同學的王子裝扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 你們也換裝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口好像太松了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要稍微提供一點服務嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是甚麼服務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將你最美麗的裝扮做為禮物送給FAN們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這樣最合適吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.00,0:12:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.98,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會是你來穿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對祐巳來說好像稍微大了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許改小一點會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.66,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.98,0:13:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會演灰姑娘現在還沒決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 祐巳也好可愛 好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.30,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 對我來說胸口實在是太鬆了一點
