Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 休息15分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 我知道你不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過能否稍微讓大家看見一點笑容？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那樣會影響到觀眾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.14,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式上場時我會好好地笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 如果有我能幫上忙的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就接受我的念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說有想拜托祐巳的事 就只有這件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真那麼討厭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.14,0:14:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 你先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.22,0:14:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.49,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.31,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 柏木同學說有話要對她講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位主角都不在 也排練不起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 稍等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.89,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.39,0:14:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想就這樣放棄排練嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子不是那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.96,0:14:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我 我也去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分頭去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.43,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人 這種時候了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡祥子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.89,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅薔薇大人與黃薔薇大人以及令也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概志摩子與由乃也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使看起來很乾練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也衹不過是高中生 所以難免會膽怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕去知道發生了甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不該去找出真相的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找祥子大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是討厭的銀杏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為那傢伙絕對不會對祥子出手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為同類所以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹甚麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 去叫守衛來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.42,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為會讓祥子大人感到為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼你會這麼想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為您臉上這樣寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.89,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚擾到大家真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才只是有點小的爭吵而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你一定要向大家說明情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.56,0:16:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木優是我的表兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只如此 他還是我的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未…婚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.99,0:16:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們即使不作戲也能互擁雙肩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是接吻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形了嗎 還不停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.36,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.82,0:17:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我也不知該怎樣才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚麼也幫不上祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.53,0:17:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是叫大家來這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.49,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人 請給我念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我改變主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.14,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…他並不喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因為我是獨生女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.93,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他有帶領小笠原集團的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙親都希望我們兩人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他才會說要和我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.58,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜歡柏木同學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.39,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自已喜歡的人並非因為喜歡自已而要與自已結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你聽我訴說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也包括我的懺悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒法向任何人訴說 所以一直很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 祥子大人 請給我念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個溫室裡半數以上的植物都是薔薇
