Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好記住這種花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
