Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可把銀杏的臭味帶入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.04,0:20:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不會再去薔薇館了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會再和祥子大人講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀演出成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演得太好了 祥子大人的灰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你發現了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.03,0:20:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.76,0:20:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在跳舞時踩了優的腳三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.65,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我能笑出來都是托祐巳的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚麼也沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能稍微陪我一會兒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.09,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 能掛在祐巳的頸上嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既非打賭 也非同情甚麼的
